{{BOLD}}<GG10>{{/BOLD}} {{BOLD}}The red Alliance places last.{{/BOLD}} The red {{LINK:#alliance}}Alliance{{/LINK}} has the right to place its {{LINK:#robot}}Robots{{/LINK}} on the Field last in {{LINK:#qualificationmatch}}Qualification Matches{{/LINK}} and {{LINK:#eliminationmatch}}Elimination Matches{{/LINK}}. Once a {{LINK:#team}}Team{{/LINK}} has placed its {{LINK:#robot}}Robot{{/LINK}} on the Field, in order to avoid schedule delays its position should not be adjusted prior to the {{LINK:#match}}Match{{/LINK}}. <GG3> applies. If a {{LINK:#team}}Team{{/LINK}} chooses to reposition their {{LINK:#robot}}Robot{{/LINK}} after it has already been placed, the opposing {{LINK:#alliance}}Alliance{{/LINK}} will also be given the opportunity to reposition their {{LINK:#robot}}Robots{{/LINK}} promptly.

{{CALLOUT}} This rule is applied differently for VEX U. See Rule <VUG1>
 {{/CALLOUT}}

